| Producer | Artifact | Consumer |
|---|---|---|
| `/plan-feature` | `{project-path}/docs/plans/{slug}.md` | `/implement` |
| `/breakdown` | `{project-path}/docs/plans/{slug}-tasks.md` | `/implement`, `/new-feature` |
| `/spike` | `{project-path}/docs/spikes/{slug}.md` | `/adr`, `/plan-feature` |
